<h2 id="how-to-use-sign-ups">How to use sign ups</h2>

<p>When using sign up it should include a heading that should clearly and concisely tell the user what they are signing up to.</p>

<h3 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h3>

<p>To ensure sign ups are accessible it is important that the input and label are connected so assisstive technologies can recognise they are connected.</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;label for="email"&gt;Enter your email address
  &lt;input type="text" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="off"&gt;
 &lt;/label&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

